    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示Alice和John之间的问候场景。Alice主动打招呼，John回应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。两个都是参与者对吧？用actor表示。那Alice第一句话的内容是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "actor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，都是actor。Alice说\"Hello John, how are you?\"，然后John回复\"Great!\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "Hello John, how are you?",
        "Great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个消息都是异步的吗？还是需要区分同步和异步？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都用异步吧，用虚线叉表示。这样看起来更像日常对话，不需要等待返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "async"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了。Alice指向John的异步消息是\"Hello John, how are you?\"，John回给Alice的异步消息是\"Great!\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "Hello John, how are you?",
        "Great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，方向好像反了。John的回复应该是从John指向Alice，不是从Alice指向John。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "John",
        "Alice",
        "Great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "抱歉，已修正。现在John的\"Great!\"正确指向Alice了。还有其他要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "John",
        "Alice",
        "Great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了，这个结构很清晰。Alice发起问候，John简短回应，符合我们的场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John"
